# Vulnerabilities in @vercel/node (devDependency) transitive packages.
# These packages are never bundled into the production SPA — they are only
# used by the Vercel CLI toolchain at build time. Production deps are clean
# (verified via `npm audit --omit=dev --audit-level=high`).
#
# To re-evaluate: run `npm audit --omit=dev` and check if any HIGH/CRITICAL
# remain. If @vercel/node ships a patched version, remove the entries below.

